# Subscriptions & Payments System — Architecture Review

## 1. Overview

This document defines the technical architecture for the Subscriptions & Payments System, enabling creators to earn through subscriptions, PPV, and tips, with weekly payouts via Square.

### Scope Summary
| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Subscriptions | Monthly + bundles (3/6/12 months) |
| PPV | Unlock individual posts |
| Tips | Send tips on posts/messages |
| Wallet | Prepaid balance for purchases |
| Payouts | Weekly payouts to creator's Square account |

### Key Decisions (Confirmed)
| Decision | Answer |
|----------|--------|
| Payment Provider | Square |
| Platform Commission | **16%** |
| Creator Earnings | **84%** |
| Payout Schedule | Weekly (Friday) |
| Minimum Payout | $20 |
| Wallet Min Top-Up | $5 |
| Wallet Structure | **Single USD balance** |
| Auto-Renew | **ON by default** |
| Email Receipts | **Yes** (all purchases) |
| Refunds | **No automated refunds** |

