## 3. Database Tables (Existing)

All required tables already exist in schema:

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `subscriptions` | User subscriptions to creators |
| `subscription_history` | Subscription lifecycle events |
| `transactions` | All financial transactions |
| `payouts` | Creator payout records |
| `ppv_purchases` | PPV content purchases |
| `tip_goals` | Creator tip goal campaigns |
| `tip_goal_contributions` | Individual tip contributions |

### Enums
- `SubscriptionPlanType`: monthly, 3month, 6month, 12month
- `SubscriptionStatus`: active, cancelled, expired, paused
- `TransactionType`: subscription, ppv, tip, message, live_tip, wallet_topup, payout, refund
- `TransactionStatus`: pending, completed, failed, refunded
- `PayoutStatus`: pending, processing, completed, failed

