## 4. API Route Structure (21 Endpoints)

### Subscriptions (5 routes)
```
POST   /api/subscriptions/[creatorId]     → Subscribe to creator
GET    /api/subscriptions                 → List user's subscriptions
PATCH  /api/subscriptions/[id]            → Cancel subscription
POST   /api/subscriptions/[id]/renew      → Renew expired subscription
GET    /api/creator/subscribers           → List creator's subscribers
```

### Payments (3 routes)
```
POST   /api/payments/checkout             → Create Square checkout
GET    /api/payments/cards                → List saved cards
POST   /api/webhooks/square/payments      → Square payment webhook
```

### Wallet (3 routes)
```
GET    /api/wallet                        → Get wallet balance
POST   /api/wallet/topup                  → Add funds to wallet
GET    /api/wallet/transactions           → Wallet transaction history
```

### PPV (2 routes)
```
POST   /api/ppv/[postId]/purchase         → Purchase PPV content
GET    /api/ppv/purchases                 → List user's PPV purchases
```

### Tips (2 routes)
```
POST   /api/tips                          → Send tip
GET    /api/tips/received                 → Creator's received tips
```

### Payouts (3 routes)
```
GET    /api/creator/payouts               → Payout history
GET    /api/creator/payouts/settings      → Get payout settings
PATCH  /api/creator/payouts/settings      → Update payout settings
```

### Transactions (3 routes)
```
GET    /api/transactions                  → User transaction history
GET    /api/creator/transactions          → Creator earnings history
GET    /api/transactions/export           → Export as CSV
```

