## 6. Square Payment Integration

### Existing Integration
- `SquareClient` already handles OAuth for creator onboarding
- Need to extend for: Checkout, Payments, Transfers

### Extended SquareClient Methods
```typescript
// Checkout (hosted payment page)
createCheckout(accessToken, { lineItems, redirectUrl }): Promise<CheckoutResult>

// Direct Payments (saved cards)
createPayment(accessToken, { amount, sourceId, customerId }): Promise<PaymentResult>
listCards(accessToken, customerId): Promise<Card[]>
saveCard(accessToken, customerId, sourceId): Promise<Card>
deleteCard(accessToken, customerId, cardId): Promise<void>

// Payouts (transfers to creator's bank)
createTransfer(accessToken, { amount, destinationId }): Promise<TransferResult>
getBankAccounts(accessToken): Promise<BankAccount[]>
```

### Payment Flow

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      SUBSCRIPTION FLOW                          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  1. User clicks "Subscribe"                                     │
│  2. Frontend calls POST /api/subscriptions/[creatorId]          │
│  3. Backend creates pending Subscription + Transaction          │
│  4. Backend creates Square Checkout (redirect_url)              │
│  5. User redirected to Square Checkout page                     │
│  6. User completes payment on Square                            │
│  7. Square webhook → POST /api/webhooks/square/payments         │
│  8. Backend updates Transaction.status = completed              │
│  9. Backend updates Subscription.status = active                │
│  10. User redirected back to creator page                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      PPV PURCHASE FLOW                          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  Option A: Pay with Wallet                                      │
│  1. Check wallet balance >= price                               │
│  2. Debit wallet                                                │
│  3. Create Transaction + PpvPurchase                            │
│  4. Grant access                                                │
│                                                                 │
│  Option B: Pay with Card                                        │
│  1. Create Square Checkout                                      │
│  2. User completes payment                                      │
│  3. Webhook creates Transaction + PpvPurchase                   │
│  4. Grant access                                                │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      PAYOUT FLOW (Weekly)                       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  1. Cron job runs every Friday at 12:00 UTC                     │
│  2. For each creator with earnings > $20:                       │
│     a. Calculate earnings for period                            │
│     b. Create Payout record (pending)                           │
│     c. Call Square API to transfer to creator's bank            │
│     d. Update Payout.status = processing                        │
│  3. Square webhook confirms transfer complete                   │
│  4. Update Payout.status = completed                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

