## 9. Security Considerations

| Concern | Mitigation |
|---------|------------|
| Payment injection | All amounts validated server-side, never trust client |
| Webhook spoofing | Verify Square webhook signatures |
| Double spending | Transaction idempotency via unique constraints |
| Unauthorized access | Check ownership on all operations |
| Race conditions | Database transactions for wallet operations |
| PCI compliance | Never store card data, use Square tokenization |

